    "Among the features passing these criteria, we performed 8 rounds of XGBoost classification within the training set, each time setting aside oncRNAs with non-zero Gini impurity index as a measure of feature importance.",
    "This resulted in obtaining an average of 6,376 ± 60 oncRNAs in each model fold and a total of 14,014 oncRNAs identified in at least 1 fold."
